{"tid":1467489,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好有必要係示威區劃位設個\"擺鬼區\"！！","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:20:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T00:02:42.000Z","uid":306803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7d2ac4e605bee764883be6ba35e60f97d3e78515","tid":1467489,"uid":306803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:20:23.000Z","msg":"大家最近都好那沉迷<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">捉鬼</span></strong></span>，我<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">明白當中既必要性</span></span></strong>，但睇完814機場live有以下感想：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1) 捉一隻鬼起碼要<ins>30個義士</ins>圍，<ins>8個記者</ins>去左影，然後隻鬼冧左仲要<ins>4-5個FA</ins>去幫，<span style=\"color: green;\">依家既做法好唔resources friendly</span><br />\n2) 發現係鬼，有好多義士都情緒激動想郁佢，但基於人道標準，成班人圍毆一個，望落我地同黑警無咩分別(重點係一開始叫記者過黎影，好多鏡頭呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，所以又<span style=\"color: green;\">內訌咁滯，對我哋義士內部嘅合作好不利</span><br />\n3) 叫記者黎影係想證明有公安/黑警/鬼混入，但最後live往往只係影到chaos，其實<span style=\"color: green;\">唔可以有系統地收集到證據</span><br />\n4) Chaos之後，<span style=\"color: green;\">隻鬼冧低左上白車就走得甩</span><br />\n5) <span style=\"color: green;\">班傳統泛民又走出黎</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有見及此，我覺得如果有以下<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">前提</span></strong>，可以劃位去整個&quot;擺鬼區&quot;：<br />\n1) <span style=\"color: purple;\">有固定既示威區</span>，並有足夠空間放係較後位置<br />\n2) <span style=\"color: purple;\">場面和理非或者夠平靜</span> (衝突緊/被衝突緊個陣就唔洗理啦屌)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>&quot;擺鬼區&quot;初步建議</strong></span>：<br />\n1) <span style=\"color: gold;\">劃特定區域</span>，室內為佳 (易守，d鬼難走佬)<br />\n2) 主要由<span style=\"color: gold;\">智者</span>(搜證同盤問)、<span style=\"color: gold;\">壯漢</span>(防止鬼攻擊人、人攻擊鬼同鬼逃走)同<span style=\"color: gold;\">醫護</span>(夠曬人道)<span style=\"color: gold;\">守住個擺鬼區</span><br />\n3) 智者唔洗多，成個場2-4人夠；壯漢就大約1壯漢對4疑鬼；FA仲簡單，1-2個想休息唔想週圍跑住既FA幫手就得<br />\n4) <span style=\"color: gold;\">真記者隨便入</span>；<span style=\"color: gold;\">其他義士就唔好入去喇</span>(除左捉疑鬼入去之外，同當然要係區外make sure佢地走唔甩)<br />\n5) 同路人發現疑似有鬼，就齊心拉佢入擺鬼區，疑鬼經<span style=\"color: gold;\">智者盤問</span>，發現<span style=\"color: gold;\">真鬼就要索帶以坐姿綁手腳</span>，唔係就放走<br />\n6) <span style=\"color: gold;\">如果係同路人既話，俾人懷疑就好好配合入擺鬼區，make sure下啫，唔好有hard feeling</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">擺鬼區既好處</span></span></strong>：<br />\n1) <span style=\"color: red;\">節省人手</span><br />\n2) <span style=\"color: red;\">減低義士內部磨擦</span><br />\n3) 大大<span style=\"color: red;\">減低team kill</span>左疑似鬼但原來唔係鬼既同路人既機會<br />\n4) 證實左係鬼既，可以放證明係佢地身前，<span style=\"color: red;\">任記者影同訪問佢地</span>，我地又可以好<span style=\"color: red;\">有系統咁收集資料再做後續跟進</span><br />\n5) <span style=\"color: red;\">減低鬼走甩既機會</span>，鬼好難再話自己受傷要上白車然後走甩(或者可以俾記者影到佢地明顯扮野都唔錯)<br />\n6) <span style=\"color: red;\">更加顯出我地有勇有謀非暴徒既特質！</span>(黑警拍馬都追唔上)<br />\n6)<span style=\"color: red;\"> 唔會因為掛住捉鬼而忘記正事！</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">捉鬼緊要，但訴求要緊！！</span></strong></span><br />\n如果各位巴絲打同意既就幫手推上熱門！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後講一句：Sor我唔係次次都發到夢！同我一直係連登係cd rom對唔住各位巴絲打！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d8714c14d8fcf923c5415fe1841ecff05a6a5bd","tid":1467489,"uid":306803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d2ac4e605bee764883be6ba35e60f97d3e78515","tid":1467489,"uid":306803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:20:23.000Z","msg":"大家最近都好那沉迷<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">捉鬼</span></strong></span>，我<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">明白當中既必要性</span></span></str